##Wuhan: "closed" in the city, not closed take-out

Micro Signal Zhenshigushi1

Function description, every day a moving original true story.

A sudden outbreak of the disease has disrupted the Spring Festival. After the city was shut down, residents were forced to stay at home and medical staff could not leave their jobs. Eating became a problem. At the same time, catering, leisure, business ultra-convenient life services industry is also facing a huge test.

As a connection point between residents and businesses, a group of stay-at-home delivery boys attached to the local life service platform came forward. After a short period of panic, they had the courage to walk through the streets, accidentally witnessing the power of a city and the goodwill of humanity. "from health care to city to service industry, the lifeline of our business partners is our lifeline, " the delivery platform ele.me concluded.
Until this epidemic is over, the only way we're gonNA get through this. We found a few takeaway riders and restaurateurs in Wuhan, and from their perspective, it was a city that struggled to suck through the haze of pneumonia.

LOCKDOWN, January 22nd-23rd

"sorry, you can not send here, you cancel the order. " On the afternoon of January 22, hungry? Delivery Clerk Chen Qi received a new order reminder. Someone ordered rice from Mr. Rice's home, delivered to the 4th floor of a civil institution building in Wuhan.

"If you don't bring me food, I'll give you a bad review! " Although the man on the other end of the phone lowered his voice, Chen Qi still heard his dissatisfaction and impatience.

A few hours earlier, ele.me had announced further measures to deal with the outbreak, including the suspension of delivery services in some sensitive areas to ensure safety.

The News of new type of coronary pneumonia is confirmed from person to person, Wuhan whole town people fall into a panic instantly. Delivery may be higher risk of infection, Chen Qi hesitated for a moment or want to refuse, apologize, explain some. At this time, the male customers tone down, reluctantly said he had been rejected twice, he was in the vicinity of the restaurant has closed, it is no way. "My kids have to eat. "

Chen Qi thought of the parents, a sudden softhearted, agreed to the distribution, wearing a two-layer mask out.

Late that night, Wuhan announced the closure of the city.

Born and raised in Wuhan, 21-year-old Chen Qi is familiar with every detail of the city as a take-out rider. He started working for a few months, originally planned to work overtime during the Spring Festival, working during the day, night home and parents reunion. A sudden outbreak of the disease threw him off his game. Now, Chen Qi is out running all day, afraid of bringing the virus home, so he continues to live in a shared house.

Under the situation, Wuhan residents are afraid to order takeout at first, Chen Qi received more than supermarkets, convenience stores "big orders. ". A 22 from the hospital's outpatient department, he rushed to the department store pick up department, the floor is filled with six snacks, bread, powder drinks big plastic bags, next to two boxes of milk. Chen Qi frowned under the brows, think it is someone go to the hospital new year, buy New Year goods.

It is raining outside, Chen Qi worried about the inconvenience of loading, to call customers to explain the distribution difficulties. Unexpectedly, a female doctor answered the phone: "We haven't eaten all the time, we are too tired, please help us bring it here. " The female Doctor Thought of Writing "20 floors" , afraid that Chen Qi would have a burden, then he said, "call me when you get to the door, and I'll go down and get it myself. "

Chen Qi a listen is a doctor's order, quickly find a roll of bandage, fixed the milk in front of the car, and with elastic band to bundle in the back of the car, ride the car started. He rode for a quarter of an hour, usually only four minutes, in case something fell off.

After unloading the goods, Chen Qi a finger to carry a thing, only out of the two little fingers, straight into the clinic side of the staff elevator. The elevator stopped at the 20th floor, Chen Qi realized that he did not disinfect, step out a step will no longer go to the department.

Out To pick up the goods is a young nurse, she walked quickly to Chen Qi in front, bent down to take things saw Chen Qi Lehong's hands, said a lot of words of thanks. Chen Qi grinned through the mask.

Walking out of the clinic building facing Jiefang Avenue, Chen Qi turned onto Xinhua road on his bicycle and glanced sideways at the fever clinic of the hospital. Usually deliver food, Chen Qi often pass by here, this old building is always very quiet, few people in and out. But on this day, the long line at the door slowly wriggled inwards, everyone wearing masks. After finishing work in the evening, Chen Qi watched the news and 473 cases were confirmed nationwide, twice as many as the previous two days.

The next morning, the station master in the Working Group as usual remind the rider on duty, before starting the site to complete the collection of masks, temperature, spray clothes disinfectant, "essential processes. ". At 10:00, public transportation in Wuhan was suspended. Empty Great Road, and the previous Spring Festival Wuhan look similar, but Chen Qi or feel particularly strange, not a taste of the year.

The night after the siege of Wuhan

#

January 24-25, New Year

Under the order of closing the city, the doors of the restaurants that had been opened sporadically closed one after another. Chinese New Year's Eve, in the front line and the fight against the epidemic of health care workers, out of the New Year's eve only biscuits, instant noodles. Fat Fat Shrimp Zhuang Shi Pai Ling Shop boss to see these pictures, heart feel bad, overnight to find someone to do 400 meals sent to the general hospital.

On New Year's Eve this year, it became a luxury to have a family reunion dinner.

Chen Qi and colleagues sent the last Lunar New Year single, respectively back to the rental housing. Roommate cooked some of his favorite dishes, and they chatted over a bottle of wine, with the gala in the background. Qin said he missed his wife and children. Laoqin was from Shandong Province. He wanted to take advantage of the new year to earn more money. He took his family to Wuhan for fun. Two children in a video call to the old Qin New Year. Chen Qi saw old Qin eyes red, and joked with him: "wait for may hot weather, no virus, then you go home. "

After the epidemic spread, ele.me and other enterprises adjusted the distribution strategy. In the closed city of Wuhan, the horsemen of ele.me were mobilized. In order to win the long war, the company for them to do a good backup support, before the city, Wuhan area has been mask, disinfectant, thermometer and other items equipped. On the first day of the Lunar New Year, city managers with emergency teams dispatched another 300,000 masks from Xiantao to make sure the supplies were ready for use by the end of February.

Like Qin, Jiang Tao, 36, was left alone in Wuhan this year. The first day of the Lunar New Year was the day when Jiang Tao and his family went from street to street to pay their respects to each other. This morning, more than 8:00, Jiang Tao took a running errands on behalf of the purchase order details listed Lianhua Qingwen capsules and other four drugs.

Jiang Tao's area of responsibility is not far from concord and Tongji. With the rapid depletion of reserves, the demand for food and medicine in residential areas has increased, but many people are afraid to go out to purchase, had to resort to take-out and on behalf of the purchase. On one occasion, he helped customers go to the supermarket to snap up 40 Jin of rice, a pot of oil, meat and vegetables, the total up front paid 1065 yuan.

Vegetables and special medicines were becoming harder to buy, and most of the nearby pharmacies were closed, but he decided to give it a try. From Jiefang Avenue to Wansongyuan residential area, and then to northwest lake, the pharmacy is either not open, or not in stock. It was almost ten o'clock and he offered to the client, "I'm near Concord, shall I go to the hospital and show you? "

The client is very surprised, emphasize to him: "that you must do a good job of protecting, the mask wears a few more. "

Ten minutes later, Jiang Tao stood in the Concord Hospital Fever Clinic Registration Team. Chaos, Jiang Tao can not think of any other way to describe it. From time to time, the sound of an ambulance sounded, wearing protective clothing of the doctor shuttling in the crowd, surrounded by patients waiting for treatment. Jiang Tao too afraid, registered, according to the nurse to find a doctor to prescribe medicine, a few words of communication, he just know the list is "epidemic" medicine. It's after 11:00.

Wuhan Union Hospital Fever Clinic

To the door of the customer, Jiangtao Dare not too close, put his hand into the medicine. The hostess did not mind opening the door, while transferring money to Jiang Tao, while asking: "Have you eaten? " "I have not seen more than 10 days of rice. " Think of their own stock of instant noodles is almost at the bottom, Jiang Tao some shame.

"I don't think you'll be able to eat either. There's nowhere to eat outside. Wait a minute, I've just saved some food. " "I'm looking at your car from above. It's hard to go to this place and that place all at once. "

Back to the dormitory at noon, Jiang Tao eat the first meal of the New Year. He sent a message to his wife, sharing the sentiment: "there are still good people in the world, AH, you pay for others, others can understand you. "

After lunch, Jiang Tao prepared to go on with his work. When I opened the APP to accept the order, a message popped up: ele.me announced the launch of the National Rider Special Care Plan, specifically seeking insurance providers for riders to take out "pneumonia insurance. ". Jiang did not look closely, as usual, to see the official prompt quickly filled out personal information, new orders waiting for him to go out.

Support January 26th-27th

The streets of Wuhan are silent on the third day of the Lunar New Year. The Gate of Laoxiangji Restaurant was opened with a bang. The staff got into the kitchen, left the stove idle for several days, and set up a casserole with hot chicken soup. More than two hours later, these meals were sent to the major hospitals in Wuhan by special bus.

Before this, the epidemic is raging, more than 100 old townsfolk chicken chain stores have closed before the festival. Like many of its peers, the national fast-food chain has been hit hard.

At a loss, the old township chicken shop director Li Shenlong saw the "medical staff can not eat" news. On New Year's Eve, many medical staff just removed from the front, on the table on the "New Year's Eve dinner" , only bucket of instant noodles.

He immediately asked for instructions to open a temporary store for the medical staff to feed. Li Shenlong wrote a long paragraph in the working group and invited his colleagues who had stayed in Wuhan to join him. As soon as the phone was put down, an employee called and said, "I can go, boss. " Li Shenlong did not immediately agree. He was afraid of the employee's impulsiveness. He repeatedly stressed the risks of staying for work, and finally asked, "still coming? "

The next morning, the staff all arrived at their posts. After ordering online, the doctor on the other end of the phone didn't have time to speak, directly cried out. However, the entire hometown chicken Wuhan region only 6 food trucks, each car can only hold more than 30. Li shenlong fought back tears and drove his private car to deliver food to the hospital.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Food for health care workers

On January 26, ele.me announced the launch of the "take-out Fast Online" service, merchants to submit business qualifications, identity information, the earliest can be applied for the same day to open a take-out service. After the message was sent out, more than a hundred restaurants, convenience stores submitted online application. The delivery riders donned helmets and face masks and set out on electric bikes to pick up the baton for the last leg of the race.

Stay in the home of the New Year Zheng Qi received an emergency order, he was temporarily transferred to the docking hungry logistics. The morning when he was supposed to sleep in was interrupted by an alarm clock. He got up and sat down at his computer. After nine o'clock in the morning, the news of the restaurant and the stationmaster poured in together. Within half an hour, the appeal of seven or eight hospitals went up.

At twelve o'clock in the afternoon, when the rush hour was over, Zheng Qi was able to take a bite to eat. Parents do not understand, tone some blame: "Why at home also busy with things? "

Zheng Qi has nothing else to do, he is busy dispatching riders. The site purchased 270 boxed meals out of its own pocket and was in urgent need of transportation to three hospitals, including Concord Hospital.

More than 2,000 orders come from the hospital every day. At first, in order to ease the concerns of the riders, ele.me platform equipped them with gloves, masks and other equipment, and took the lead in the industry to develop a "peace of mind" product to support "no contact" food delivery, just put the food at the hospital gate, another PEP rally in the group.

A list of riders is collected before the delivery, and each time the stationmaster sends the hospital's delivery requests to the work group, 30 seconds later, all the riders have been collected at the bottom, faster than any other type of order.

Near the meal point, there are several blue electric cars parked outside the clinic building of Concorde Hospital. Chourret, the rider, was a little apprehensive as he approached the gate. The hospital had set up a quarantine zone, and the riders simply stood in the distance, waiting for the nurses to come down and get their food. Nevertheless, the family did not agree with him to go to the hospital and other places, in order to normal food delivery, Chourret had to hide the family.

Dozens of boxes barely fit in the cardboard boxes, and only two nurses came downstairs to pick up the food. After picking up the bag, the nurses told him that, until then, the hospital had to rely on biscuits and instant noodles. The intensity of the work is too great for the nutrition of the medical staff to keep up. The nurse's words left him feeling sour, guilt and a sense of responsibility that gradually repelled the fear of the virus.

Strength January 28th-29th

On January 29, the number of confirmed cases reached 3,554 in Hubei Province, and the outbreak escalated again.

To the outside world, Wuhan is a dangerous city. And the caterers who serve know best that disaster will pass, and that warmth and power are slowly being restored to the city.

Wuhan residents, stunned by the outbreak, began to show their concern for frontline staff in their own way. During the first seven days of the siege, ele.me's take-out list had 5,504 orders with the words "refueling in Wuhan" and 4,563 with the words "attention to the epidemic" . A rider passes Wuhan Aijia International Huacheng. As darkness falls, he lights a cigarette and sits by the side of the road. Suddenly behind the building came the intermittent shouting: "Wuhan REFUELS! " He lowered the head to wipe the eye: "Damn, smoked the eye. "

Chen Qi is also in the delivery, received such warmth. On the 29th, he received an order from Vanke community. The message read: "after delivery, just hang it at the door. There are people who are hot in the house. It is not convenient to open the door. " When he arrived at the customer's door, he saw two masks specially prepared by the customer for him.

Chen Qi noticed that several residents who lived in isolation at home would take special note of their New Year wishes. Data shows that up to the fourth day of the Lunar New Year, Wuhan has 1289 ele.me order take-out appeared "happy New Year / Happy New Year" . It turns out that the lost flavor of the year has been preserved in another form. With no family around, many people are spending this special year together.

Some users repeatedly ordered from Li Shenlong's store. "The lunch was the best meal I've had in two days. I was about to cry when I ate that fish, " the woman in the black down jacket said. She didn't know what to say, i could only clap the nurse's hand and comfort her repeatedly.

Pay Back, Li Shenlong store docking hospital from the beginning of four or five to more than 10, chicken's more than 10 chain stores also resumed operation.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Photo gallery: Chicken provides meals for hungry bikers

Thanks to the platform side of the policy, many and the same chicken restaurant service business recovery. ELE.ME's local life service company, Ali, made the "five decisions" in a timely manner. In addition to the fast launch of the merchant's take-out service, in addition, merchants'commission, annual fee extension, loan financial support and up to 300,000 yuan of pneumonia insurance will be given. Alibaba group partner, Alibaba Local Life Services Company President Wang Lei explained, platform and business auxiliary car, "We believe in the strength of mutual help, business partners lifeline is our lifeline. "

The day before yesterday, Chen Qi in the door of the supermarket waiting for Pie orders, a 60-year-old man recruited him to help. I went out to buy food by myself, but I couldn't carry it after paying the bill. Chen Qi is not busy, so for GRANDPA to the food to a kilometer away from the community, moved to the fifth floor.

"thank you, young people really good. " Uncle insisted to reward, Chen Qi declined. GRANDPA took out a red envelope from his pocket and said he must accept it. It was a New Year's wish. Chen Qi guessed that this should be for the grandson has not been reunited. He took the red envelope and gave the old man a year of worship.
